   <head>
      <att>align</att>
      <seg type="fullName">Alignment</seg>
   </head>
   <div type="summary">
      <p>Horizontal position of the text within a column, indicating whether text
                        should be displayed flush left, flush right, centered in the column, or
                        justified (flush both left and right). Available in <gi>colspec</gi> ,
                           <gi>entry</gi>, and <gi>tgroup</gi>. </p>
   </div>
   <div type="values">
      <p>left, right, center, justify, char</p>
   </div>
</div>
